2019-09-09  Reini Urban  <rurban@cpan.org>

	preview is embedded in sentinels

	dwgbmp: support optional 2nd arg bmpfile
	as documented

	dwgbmp: fix for 64bit
	on 64bit long is wrong, need BITCODE_RL sizes.

