	for VERTEX_2D and VERTEX_3D samples (which crash on DXFIN import)

	decode VALUE_HANDLE_N: [vcount]: NULL HANDLE
	itemhandles[vcount]: NULL HANDLE(2) [0]
	vs
	itemhandles[vcount][15]: 2 HANDLE(2.1.66) absolute:66 [0]

