	dwgwrite: fix wrong infile check (#77)
	Thanks to @shlyakpavel

	fix dwggrep NULL deref (#77)
	Thanks to @shlyakpavel

	fix NULL deref (#77)
	added recently. Thanks to @shlyakpavel

