2018-07-05  Reini Urban  <rurban@cpan.org>

	unknown: implemented log_unknown_dxf.pl
	created now alldxf.inc with all the real dxf values to find
	in the unknown bits.

	DEBUGGING_CLASSES ASSOCACTION, ASSOCNETWORK

